*My Memories of Old Beijing. Tr. Nancy Ing and Chi Pang-yuan. HK: Chinese University Press, 1992. Excerpted as &quot;Memories of Old Peking: Huian Court.&quot; Tr. Cathy Poon. Renditions, 27–28 (1987): 19–48.

